path.id: Google Developer Student Clubs (GDSC) are community groups for students from any academic background in their undergraduate or graduate term. By joining GDSC, students build their professional and personal network, get access to Google Developer Resources, and work together to build solutions for local problems in a peer - to - peer learning environment.
